Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Nami! Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I see an island below that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to land there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why've you not reported to me after\Nfinding the Millennial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our main forces will now\Nhead for Warship Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Nami makes the\Nmen do all the work...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Less complaining\Nand more pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start getting cocky, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're alive... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Showdown in the Ruins!\NTense Zoro vs. Eric!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a huge picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like some\Nsort of map... Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too worn out\Nto make any sense of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is this place, anyways?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this supposed\Nto be the dragons' nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Apis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu says he doesn't\Nknow what this place is, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! He's always just a useless old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how exactly are you being useful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me?!\N--Hey, guys! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling picture's fallen down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yikes!\N--It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, talk about dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole building's ready to fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we dilly-dally around here,\Nwe'll be in danger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the heck outta this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this might be the dragons' nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any dragons\Naround here, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might not be Lost Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know the reason why!\NQuit making stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell that, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the ceiling picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely. It's a map that marks\Nthe location of Lost Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That island with a\Ndome-shaped building on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's this island.\NThat dome is this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does look just like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the people around the island\Nare the people who once lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd wager they're probably Apis' ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ancestors?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you remember what\Nold man Bokuden told us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I was asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now! He said\Nthe people of Warship Island
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had traveled there from another island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nhe did say something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean the dynasty\Nhe kept blabbing on about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what had me wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were all the dragon statues\Nand paintings on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they might've been used\Nby the people living on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to worship the Millennial Dragon as a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the Millennial Dragon used\Nto fly over this island long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would lower the chance of the\Ndragons' nest being on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...! If so, then where's the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be that island\Nwith the dragon drawn on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:06:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an island ahead of where\Nthis island's people are praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real Lost Island!\NThe dragons' nest must be there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!\NThat island is shaped like...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming the map is correct,\Nthe dragons' nest is on Warship Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought there were no places\Non Warship Island that fit the bill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what the map says!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you saying the people\Nlong ago just drew random nonsense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san'd never say\Nanything that's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means it's somewhere on that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll figure it out if we go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... It could also have sunk\Nto the bottom of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's actually much more likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would explain why\Nnobody's ever found it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think back, Grandpa Ryu!\NWhere is the dragons' nest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it was this place,\Nbut there's nothing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only a painting, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the painting bring\Nback any memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only hope now is that you\Nremember something, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Please!\NRemember, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! So the dragons' nest\Nreally is on Warship Island, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! How did you know\Nwhat he said, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.\NGrandpa Ryu said he remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says the dragons' nest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is on an island east of a peak\Nthat looks like a warship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! Why does he say that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only after we went through\Nall that hardship to get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for dragging\Nyou all the way out here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for something that might've\Nalready sunk into the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? The dragons' nest\Ncould be somewhere unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no telling for sure\Nwithout checking it out, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being discouraged this\Neasily isn't like you, Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get anything done\Nif you're afraid of failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with\Nliving a roundabout life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's go! Grandpa Ryu won't\Nget any better if we just stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:10:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know where to find\NDragonite and the dragons' nest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no point if it's\Nat the bottom of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem my only option\Nis to take your Millennial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we don't know if their\Nnest is on the ocean bottom or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he had Sickle-Sickle\NFruit powers, if I recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one nasty guy we got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickle-Sickle Fruit?!\NHe has Devil Fruit powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey...\N--Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead and take\NGrandpa Ryu to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Whoa, now! The ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know\Nwhere the exit here is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can just... make one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not seriously gonna--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought that would\Nbust it open, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open! It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked out! It worked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's less than a caveman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, Luffy! Get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast! So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We always make it out alive, don't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for certain that we'll\Nlive through this! That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes going back a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Get in my way\Nand you'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's see how you plan\Non making me pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty confident that right now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're the fastest moving\Nthings in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of thing is that to brag about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna wind up in pieces\Nbefore we get to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickle-Sickle Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to be playing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only goal is that Millennial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Will Zoro really be alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's up against a guy\Nwith Devil Fruit powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't stand a chance,\Nno matter how strong he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll still be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Ahead! Ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give us that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:15:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't let you pass here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. It's up to me\Nwhether I pass or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! That nimble bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm not letting you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! There's another dead-end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wanna bust it down?\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that up ahead is\Nthe cliff we followed on our way up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, we'll fall over it\Nhead-first and then we're goners!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Think we can fly?\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now die like a good little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we somehow\Nmanaged to make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we seriously have\Nincredible luck or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We made it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to set sail! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally... gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says... He says Zoro's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?! We gotta help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bingo!\N--Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not this pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here we go!\N--I told you to stop doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, someday\NI will chop this guy up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to let you escape me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're out! We're out!\N--That's definitely weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! They're on their\Nway to Warship Island again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the Millennial Dragon in tow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then make chase the moment\Nwe're ready! On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir! A-And one other\Nthing, Lt. Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While in pursuit of them,\NEric-sama also reappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has just returned to ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of useless clods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just sink the lot of 'em...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Thank you for the report!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you've\Nreturned to the ship unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get the Dragonite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time for sarcastic remarks,\Nthen go after them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at 'em come! Look at 'em come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never catch up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry is faster and\Nmore agile than bulky Navy warships,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what are we going to do\Nwhen we get to Warship Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll be okay!\N--How will we be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to find\Nthe dragons' nest first
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Grandpa Ryu can get better, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easier said than done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their nest could be\Nat the bottom of the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to search the\Nbottom of the ocean then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's big talk for\Nsomeone who can't swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, we need to get back\Nas fast as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to be\Nmessing with the navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san. It doesn't look like\Nthat's going to be an option...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a gargoyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The small fries have leapt forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open to the left and right!\NCrane Wing Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many ships\Ndoes the damn navy have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connect all ships by chain links\Nto create a complete wall
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that won't allow even a\Nsingle small fry to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?! They have us blocked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump onto a ship, kick the guys off,\Nand cut the links!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only choice, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You can do that, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Luffy! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound too bad to me, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! But, are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you could\Nsurvive if you tried that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Apis. Things'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But make it quick, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, take aim!\NThe target is the pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do not hit the raft behind the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must not be damaged\Nin even the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, full stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nelson Royal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had you pegged as a fatty\Nwho can do nothing but eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when you're on the sea,\Nit's as if you've been reborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mere commodore,\Nbut a commodore nonetheless, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.34,0:23:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:23:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna take us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell thought\Nof this plan anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ride's about to get rough!\NHang on to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.82,0:24:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that round is gonna hit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your blabbing and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,0:24:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.49,0:24:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.82,0:24:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy, Completely Surrounded!\NCommodore Nelson's Secret Strategy"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
